  <brief_title>The Effect of a Multispecies Probiotic on Hypersensitivity in Irritable Bowel Syndrome (IBS) Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of a Multispecies Probiotic on Hypersensitivity in IBS Patients</official_title>
