  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether a specifically designed multispecies
      probiotic decreases visceral hypersensitivity in IBS-patient (defined by an increased pain
      tolerance threshold). Moreover, the effect on general symptom scores and inflammatory and
      microbiological parameters will be studied.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
